"Marks {{{
" Highlight words to avoid in tech writing
" http://css-tricks.com/words-avoid-educational-writing/
runtime plugin/mark.vim
silent MarkClear

"bad words
Mark /\cobviously\|basically\|simply\|of\ scourse\|clearly\|just\|everyone\sknows\|however\|so,\|easy/
Mark /\obviamente\|basicamente\|simplesmente\|com\ certeza\|claramente\|apenas\|todos\sabem\|entretanto\|então,\|fácil/

"worng patterns
Mark /\w\s\{2,\}\w\|\s\+$\|\v<(\w+)\_s+\1>/
"}}}

